3
00:00:16,717 --> 00:00:17,717
<i>Che...</i>

4
00:00:18,206 --> 00:00:19,206
<i>succede?</i>

5
00:00:21,544 --> 00:00:23,544
Meruem, Re delle Formichimere,

6
00:00:24,363 --> 00:00:27,210
